Thancred Waters (GNB)
Weapon type: Sword
Crystal Color: White
Spheres: A A B

Skill 1: Keen Edge Combo
 7-Hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Increases Cartidge count by 1.
 Grants [Camouflage] to self for 2 turns.
 Uses: 7
15cp: High Steel Gunblade
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Increases base duration of [Camouflage] by 2 turns
Burst Strike:
 +Increases BRV potency
c.55: Keen Edge Combo Extend
 +Adds 1 use
 +Becomes a 4-hit Melee BRV+HP attack triggered twice
 +Grants BRV to self based on HP damage dealt after both HP attacks (20%)
 +Increases BRV and HP damage reduction effects of [Camouflage] by 10%
Burst Strike:
 +Increases BRV gain based on Max BRV (+10%)
 +Becomes a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Extends duration of all self buffs by 1 turn

[Camouflage]: Reduces BRV and HP damage taken by 20%.

Powder Gauge: Holds 2 cartridges.
When Cartridge count is 0 or greater:
 -Prevents KO if HP is at least 50% of Max HP and leaves HP value at 1
When Cartridge count>0:
 -Follows Demon Slaughter with Fated Circle
 -Changes HP Attack, HP Attack+ to Burst Strike
 -If HP drops below 5%, reduces own HP to 1 and triggers Superbollide

Burst Strike: Consumes 1 Cartridge.
              Gain BRV based on Max BRV (40%).
              1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
              Recovers BRV to self based on HP Damage dealt (50%)
Fated Circle: Consumes 1 Cartridge.
              Gain BRV based on Max BRV (40%).
              1-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack.
              Deals split HP damage.
Superbollide: Consumes 1 Cartridge.
              Grants BRV to self based on HP Damage taken in last 2 turns (30%)
              Grants [Superbollide] to self for 2 turns
[Superbollide]: Nullifies all incoming damage to self.

