Skill 3: Cartridge Boost Up
 Increases Cartidge count by 2.
 Increases party's Max BRV by 10% for 4 turns.
 Uses: 3

EX: Weathered Lionheart
 +Equips EX ability Wicked Talon Combo
Grants [No Mercy] to self for 6 turns.
2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack triggered 4 times.
Grants BRV to self based on TOTAL HP damage dealt after each HP attack (20%).
