-Wicked Talon Combo+
Grants [No Mercy] to self for 6 turns.
2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack triggered 7 times.
Grants BRV to self based on TOTAL HP damage dealt after each HP attack (20%).
Consumes 1 Cartridge.
 Recast: Slow
  -LB1: BRV damage increase (10%)
  -LB2: Prevents BREAK if BRV is at least 50% of Max BRV and leaves BRV value at 1
  -LB3: Recast Up (10%)
 EX+: Increases BRV potency
      When Cartridge count is 0:
      -Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+
      -Turns HP Attack to HP Attack+
      When Cartridge count is greater than 0:
      -Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack++
  -LB1: Increases own ATK (30%) and Max BRV (40%)
  -LB2: At QUEST Start:
        -Grants [No Mercy] to self for 6 turns
        -Cartridge Count starts at 1
        -First turn has no Action Delay and does not increase Turn counter
        -Will not consume skill uses on first turn
  -LB3: When using Wicked Talon Combo/+:
        -Increases BRV potency tremendously
        -Allows for 150% Stolen BRV Overflow
        -Allows for 120% Gained BRV Overflow
        When using Wicked Talon Combo+:
        -Increases BRV gained based on TOTAL HP damage dealt (+20%)
        -Removes target's BREAK status before attacking

[No Mercy]: ATK Up (50%), Max BRV Up (50%)
            Stolen BRV Overflow Up (30%)
            BRV Damage Taken Down (30%)
BRV Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV attack
             Increases Cartidge count by 1
BRV Attack++: 3-hit Melee BRV attack
              Increases Cartidge count by 1
HP Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
            Allows for 120% Stolen BRV Overflow

